#: input:6 standard
msgid ""
"Amidst the dunes—a small rocky outcrop; the Romans have a long way to go—"
"will they make it? <br> <br>Version 2.01"
msgstr ""

#: input:7 input:13 standard
msgid ""
"Use the single—or better yet, the double—siege rampart for protection by "
"keeping enemy stonemasons away from it."
msgstr ""
"Gebruik de enkele—of beter nog, de dubbele—belegeringswal als bescherming "
"door vijandelijke steenhouwers ervan weg te houden."
